txt.en: Not only are there worms within the western valley of Ram Dúath, but drakes as well. The winged drakes, more intelligent than their lesser kin, present a greater threat to Esteldín and the North Downs.

Drake-nests may be found in the western valley of Ram Dúath, north of Esteldín.\n\nYou should destroy the nests of the drakes who dwell within the western valley of Ram Dúath before they can multiply.
